It's forgotten.

24:24.162 --> 24:25.495
And I want you
to forget that
you work for me.

24:25.564 --> 24:26.997
It's forgotten.
And I want you to forget

24:27.066 --> 24:28.198
that I'm twice
as big as you are.

24:28.267 --> 24:29.899
It's forgotten.

24:29.968 --> 24:31.101
Gilligan,
what did you think

24:31.170 --> 24:33.070
