little buddy?

24:33.139 --> 24:34.671
It's forgotten.

24:34.740 --> 24:35.772
Come on now,
gilligan.

24:35.841 --> 24:37.474
What did you
really think?

24:37.542 --> 24:39.276
Terrible, terrible,
terrible.

24:39.344 --> 24:40.577
Don't pay
any attention to him.

24:40.646 --> 24:41.979
He just says
what he's taught.

24:42.048 --> 24:44.647
Uh-huh. And who's
been teaching him?

